---
import Card__Risk from "./card__risk.astro";
import icon1 from "../assets/icon 1.svg";
import image1 from "../assets/image1.png";
---

<section
    id="risk"
    class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center h-auto lg:py-24 w-full pt-8 pb-10 gap-6"
>
    <article
        class="w-full h-auto flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-2 px-4"
    >
        <h2
            class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-medium text-white-700 uppercase font-bebas-neue leading-tight lg:leading-14 mt-2 text-left lg:text-center w-full"
        >
            Institutional Risk & Governance Framework
        </h2>
        <p
            class="text-gray-300 lg:mt-3 text-sm md:text-base text-left lg:text-center w-full lg:w-2/3"
        >
            Risk oversight, compliance monitoring, and operational controls are
            embedded across our ecosystem, providing intermediaries with the
            transparency and discipline required for long‑term capital
            preservation
        </p>
    </article>
    <article
        class="w-full h-full flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-end px-4 justify-center gap-4"
    >
        <Card__Risk
            title="Governance Committees"
            description="Board‑level committees oversee risk, compliance, and operational integrity. Clear separation exists between executive functions and oversight roles"
            icon={icon1.src}
            image={icon1.src}
        />
        <Card__Risk
            title="AML/CTF Framework"
            description="Comprehensive anti‑money laundering and counter‑terrorism financing protocols, including intermediary due diligence, transaction monitoring, and regulatory"
            icon={icon1.src}
            icon={icon1.src}
            image={image1.src}
        />
        <Card__Risk
            title="Operational Controls"
            description="Daily position reconciliations, segregation verification, and independent audit trails maintain accuracy and transparency across custody and trading operations"
            icon={icon1.src}
            image={icon1.src}
        />
        <Card__Risk
            title="Risk Oversight"
            description="Proprietary risk models and internal monitoring ensure market discipline without exposure to client assets. No client funds are held or traded"
            icon={icon1.src}
            image={icon1.src}
        />
    </article>
</section>
